			<description><![CDATA[<h1>Credit—What You Need to Know</h1>
<p>Credit plays an important role in our lives. Without it, life gets  complicated. You might even miss money-saving opportunities. For  example, few can afford to buy a home or car with cash; most take out a  loan to do that. Some employers run credit checks on potential employees  as a way to screen them, especially if they are handling cash or  working with sensitive customer information.</p>
<p><span> </span></p>
